nodes.caption: WELLNESS WEDNESDAY✨✨ There may be many reasons (excuses) as to why we don't make healthy choices. Some say it's time, or maybe cost. To debunk the TIME EXCUSE, we all have the same 24 hours in a day. To debunk the COST EXCUSE, there are too many healthy inexpensive food options available now AND it costs nothing to go outside and MOVE. So, those excuses don't really work 😐 I believe the underlying issue is rooted in lack of love or self care for ourselves. We have to get to the place where we truly know WE are worth the effort, our HEALTH is worth the effort. In order to be the BEST versions of ourselves, we HAVE TO start with LOVE and CARE of ourselves. ❤ #health #wellness #worth #bestversionofyou #lifestyle #consistency #effort #noexcuses #love #selfcare #valueyou #fitness #fitspo #fitfam #fitnessmotivation #fitnessjourney #yourlife #personaltrainer #jeaninelynnfitness #fitchick #fitgirl #ladieswholift #eathealthy #healthyfood #westlakevillage #agourahills #thousandoaks #simivalley #conejovalley
